OL,3,CSchool crossing patrollers facing
OL,4,Cabusive language and aggressive driving
OL,6,FHe said "speed is one of the issues"
OL,7,Fwith "people not wanting to stop" and
OL,8,Fdriving down the wrong side of the
OL,9,Froad.
OL,11,F"I've had one trying to push me out of
OL,12,Fthe way but they suffer because I just
OL,13,Fstay there, I make sure they wait.
OL,15,F"You can't give into them, you have
OL,16,Fgot to be thick skinned if you know
OL,17,Fwhat I mean," he said.
