OL,3,CSchool crossing patrollers facing
OL,4,Cabusive language and aggressive driving
OL,6,FParents say he provides a vital
OL,7,Fservice, with one adding: "Cars come
OL,8,Fdown here really, really quickly so if
OL,9,Fwe didn't have him it would be
OL,10,Fimpossible for us to get into school."
OL,12,FSchool crossing patrollers have the
OL,13,Fsame authority to stop the traffic as
OL,14,Fpolice officers and failing to stop
OL,15,Fwhen asked can result in three penalty
OL,16,Fpoints, a fine of up to a #1,000 and
OL,17,Feven disqualification.
